      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SOME AMERICAN (4) beat some good rivals when he scored a resuming win here last time out, leading from one spot wider and finishing 2.5 metres ahead of his rivals. Should be improved and has the talent to take out a race like this. ITS CONFIDENTIAL (9) was held up and far from disgraced in open company last week. Had scored a resuming win in Sydney prior and showed his talent when he won the Vicbred Super Series 3CG Final here last season. Loves this distance, winning seven of 11 attempts. Threat. FORTY LOVE (5) wasn't too far behind ITS CONFIDENTIAL last week. This shorter distance may suit better. SWEET IDEAL (3) is better served returning to the front line having come from this barrier when she won three back at this circuit and distance. CALEXICO (8) draws for a trail and could be dangerous with his A-game.",
